
DEUS, qui sanctum Joánnem, Confessórem atque Doctórem, perféctæ sui abnegatiónis et Crucis amatórem exímium effecísti: concéde; ut, ejus imitatióni júgiter inhæréntes, glóriam assequámur ætérnam. Per Dóminum.
O GOD, who didst endow holy John thy Confessor with a wondrous love of self-denial and of the cross; grant that we, steadfastly following his example, may attain unto eternal glory. Through our Lord.
